          <div type="edition"><ab>
 <lb n="1"/>*** wa ǧaʿala nī ăl lāhu fidāʾa ka 
 <lb n="2"/>ʾuḥibbu ǧaʿala nī ăl lāhu fidāʾa ka ʾan tadfaʿa 
 <lb n="3"/>ʾilà ăl ǧāriyaẗi dirhamayni wa ṯulṯā 
 <lb n="4"/>li taṣrifa ḏālika fī ḥawāʾiǧa 
 <lb n="5"/>wa tuʿarrif nī ḫabara ka bi mašīʾati ka 
   </ab></div>
 <div type="translation"><ab>
		 <lb n="1"/>
 	  [... and may God make me your ra]nsom.
		 <lb n="2"/>
 	  I should like you - may God make me your ransom - to
		 <lb n="3"/>
 	  pay to the slave-girl two dirhams and two thirds
		 <lb n="4"/>
 	  so that she may spend it for necessities
		 <lb n="5"/>
 	  and inform me of your news as far as you wish (to do so).
 </ab></div>
